"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bach is due to hand over tothe IOC's first female president, Kirsty Coventry, next week.\", \"from\": 2119, \"to\": 2207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2119, \"end\": 2123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 0.9999999981180281, \"rank\": 1.881865492156026e-09, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}, {\"begin\": 2150, \"end\": 2153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.2773993580783215e-17, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2180, \"end\": 2195, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kirsty_Coventry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kirsty Coventry\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kirsty_Coventry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kirsty_Coventry\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He added: \\\"I have every confidence that she will take the organisation into a new era - united in our commitment to the values that have guided us for over a century.\\\"\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2376, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Share this article  Subscribe to the City AM newsletter to have our top stories delivered directly to your inbox.\", \"from\": 2378, \"to\": 2491, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow us for breaking news and latest updates\", \"from\": 2493, \"to\": 2539, \"entities\": []}]}"